'''Dr. Campbell''' is a cardiothoracic surgeon at St. Ambrose Hospital.

==History==
When [[Troy Hagen]] came into the hospital after collapsing at [[Oceanside Wellness Group]], Dr. Campbell ran scans and diagnosed coronary artery disease, for which she planned bypass surgery. However, she missed a pseudoaneurysm on the scans that could have killed Troy if Sam had not pointed it out.

==Career==
She is a cardiothoracic surgeon at [[St. Ambrose Hospital]].
